{"tid":580571,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測) 逃出魔幻紀1-3","createTime":"2018-03-04T15:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T19:34:07.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53951d755e7fd38dd727353af620433d8f31033a","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:19:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=i39qNLC40jzU861zNgQnlnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=14fb37fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=i39qNLC40jzU861zNgQnlnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=82c47a63\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/64/ZathuraPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F64%2FZathuraPoster.jpg&h=a9f1f082&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b6/Jumanji_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb6%2FJumanji_poster.jpg&h=8a2e6801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/13/Jumanji_Welcome_to_the_Jungle_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F13%2FJumanji_Welcome_to_the_Jungle_Poster.jpg&h=ff8703b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.這並不是一般的棋藝遊戲，驚險刺激而魅力所在是可以體驗前所未有的冒險，像是家中出現獅子、猴子、叢林裡各式各樣的生物，甚至是把玩家傳送到未知的非洲叢林。參與者的代價是遊戲開始便要走畢全程才能離開。<br />\n12歲的亞倫與莎拉在偶然機會下參與了這個亡命的遊戲棋玩意，怪事發生，亞倫被攝進魔幻世界中，突然人間蒸發。26年後，一對小姐弟茱蒂與彼得搬到亞倫的舊居，意外地將亞倫在棋中世界釋放出來。同時棋裡的原始猛獸亦一併來到人類世界並進行破壞。拯救世界的方法便是找回莎拉，完成當年未下完的棋⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n2.描述兩個老是吵鬧不休的兄弟，在玩一個他們在老家地下室發現的神祕的遊戲時，進入了最黑暗的太空深處。現在他們必須克服他們的差異，並且同心協力完成遊戲，不然他們就會永遠被困在外太空了。<br />\n在他們的父親（提姆&middot;羅賓斯）出門上班之後，把他們留給他們的姊姊（克莉絲汀&middot;史都華）照顧，六歲大的丹尼（強納&middot;波波）和十歲大的華特（喬許&middot;哈契森）不是搞的彼此神經緊張，就是根本無聊的半死<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述四名青少年男女在清理學校的地下室的同時，他們找到了一套古老的電子遊戲機《野蠻遊戲》，試圖遊玩的四人卻意外地被吸入遊戲世界中，為此展開一場瘋狂的叢林歷險<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=i39qNLC40jzU861zNgQnlnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f12a7af6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=i39qNLC40jzU861zNgQnlnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4713004b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1123743de8b9bf621690a03890e26003f0d03aff","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8667e1ebec96d3b81041b8aba34bf645f1d47a2","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4951fbe3f5088f258a34f233bd9d930d856bfa93","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccff1a8f3d99a1330245b42130761758516c9d33","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfa3d189f7962ced038c1e05785af28a72c28d0","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1031337d91e1a889ee3f991e65469b920a8c2c","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b20593c8a5745d9ec131057a115676a3f5cc2a","tid":580571,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}